{
  "stem": "21354.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Britain did their share for me, and I was anxious to do my share for Britain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Simple.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no contact at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "None.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Occasionally one could sort of put a card through the Red Cross, which went over another country.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But basically, there was no communication.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the same.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were many subjects, many subjects.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But basically, my interest was simple-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to join the war and to fight for Britain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had other interests.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Others want to leave Britain, wanted to go to Israel, to Palestine, to New Zealand, to Canada.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We only lived in hope.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had hope, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had hope.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We genuinely believed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One also did hear that somebody got out over Holland and they got here, and we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Air Force.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like every young man, my dream was to be a pilot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That-- that dream soon came to an end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a matter of a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After I had done my initial training, I had-- we were tested, and I was found to be colorblind.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good examination.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They sent me to Blackpool.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was examined by top surgeons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was colorblind and, as such, unfit to be a pilot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My next job, what could I do to fly?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could be a mechanic, you could be a-- so I joined to be a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did my training, became an Air Force flight mechanic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned all about engines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I did my test flights, because the Royal Air Force had adopted a wonderful scheme.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When you serviced an aircraft and it was taken for test, all the mechanics who worked on that aircraft had to go up with it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because if it would fall, they would fall down first.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
